">
<p><strong>Input:</strong><span class="example-io" style="
    font-family: Menlo,sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
"> energy = [-2,-3,-1], k = 2</span></p>

<p><strong>Output:</strong><span class="example-io" style="
    font-family: Menlo,sans-serif;
